title: #92Noon! VikingsTalkers/Gene/Leber/Zimm/Burns
description:
Beating the Bengals and Sunday's game take up most of the first hour, followed by Bucs vox Gene Deckerhoff!
Leber on the hotline and Zimmer's X's & O's chat get us midway thru before Ryan Burns offers Gophers opinions during the final hour. Show wraps with some NFL picks for the weekend.
